 governance, a draft toolkit on investigating mining sector related cases was developed. Results from this project are now incorporated in country-level initiatives (for example: the joint UNDP and Swedish Environment Protection Agency project, \"Environmental Governance for Sustainable Natural Resources\" in Mongolia). 21 Publications and Knowledge Products for 2016 Achieving the Sustainable Development Goals in the Era of the Addis Ababa Action Agenda: Progress on establishing integrated national financing frameworks in the Asia-Pacific region Access and Delivery Partnership (ADP) Status Report 2015 Being LGBTI in China: A National Survey on Social Attitudes towards Sexual Orientation, Gender Identity and Gender Expression Access and Delivery Partnership (ADP) Status Report 2016 Conflict Prevention and Peacebuilding Work in Asia Pacific Case Study - The Philippines: Participatory Monitoring Case Study - Thailand Refuse to be Corrupt Caf\u00e9 22 Human Traficking Vulnerabilities in Asia: A Study on Forced Marriage Between Cambodia and China Development Finance for the 8th National Socio-Economic Development Plan and SDGs in Lao PDR Guidelines for the Examination of Patent Applications relating to Pharmaceuticals The Hidden Pearls: Heroic Stories of Women Peace Builders A Pipeline Analysis of New Products for Malaria, TB and NTDs: A Working Paper Promoting and Protecting Human Rights: Sexual Orientation, Gender Identity and Sex Characteristics Publications and Knowledge Products for 2016 23 Strengthening Finance for the 7th Five Year Plan and SDGs in Bangladesh Stories of Intersex People from Nepal Training Manual: Empowering Women Affected by HIV to Protect their Rights at Health Care Settings A Transparent and Accountable Judiciary to Deliver Justice for All Review of Country Progress in Addressing Legal and Policy Barriers to Universal Access to HIV Services in Asia and the Pacific Publications and Knowledge Products for 2016 Switched On: Youth at the Heart of Su